

1. Give me the count of links on the page?
A: driver.findElements(By.tagName("a")).size();


2. count of links only from footer section?
A: 		limiting webdriver scope means :: creating a mini driver and then getting the links list

		WebElement footerdriver = driver.findElement(By.id(footer section id));
		footerdriver.findElements(By.tagName("a")).size();
		
		
		
3. count of links of one column from footer section
A: WebElement columndriver = footerdriver.findElement(By.xpath("//td//ul"));		
   coloumndriver.findElements(By.tagName("a")).size();
		
